inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
union pageViews,customEvents
| where timestamp between(datetime("2019-02-01T03:51:36.396Z")..datetime("2019-02-02T03:51:36.396Z"))
| where (customDimensions["UserAgent"] == "AzurePowershell/Az1.0.0") and (customDimensions["ModuleName"] contains "Accounts") 
| summarize Ocurrences=count() by tostring(customDimensions["Command"]) , tostring(customDimensions["IsSuccess"])
| order by Ocurrences desc
| render barchart
